714623f-a.title: Manhattan: 82nd Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
714623f-a.text:
East 82nd Street, at, adjoining and west of the S.W. corner of
Third Ave. No. 178 East 82nd Street, adjoining the corner is a 2S
story building; of which the upper half is of wood.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 244.
